            // built_in: 'EXTRACT',
            type: "CENTURY DAY DECADE DOW DOY EPOCH HOUR ISODOW ISOYEAR MICROSECONDS MILLENNIUM MILLISECONDS MINUTE MONTH QUARTER SECOND TIMEZONE TIMEZONE_HOUR TIMEZONE_MINUTE WEEK YEAR"
